data.description: Executive style beautiful POOL home located in a perfect spot just on the outskirts of WestChase with easy access to both Hillsborough & Pinellas counties.  This 4 bedroom, 3 bath & 2 car garage is showcased on an oversized corner homesite with an extensive landscaping package.  Elevation is upgraded & outlined nicely with brick & shutters.  Fabulous home to dress to impress with its high ceilings, spacious formal dining room, & generous sized entertaining room overlooking the pool & housing a fireplace for those cooler evenings.  Equally impressive kitchen with raised panel & staggered cabinets some up to 48" in height.  Complementary GRANITE countertop & STAINLESS STEEL appliances.  Stay organized with the included home management center.  Discreet doggie/kitty door to allow your pets to do their business on their time.  First floor guest suite with a full bath.  Family bedrooms located on 2nd floor with master suite including en-suite, 2 spacious secondary bedrooms separated by nice size secondary bathroom. Customer friendly staircase with 2 landings.  NO CARPET in the home!  Upgraded pavers & coping on the driveway & pool area.  Included solar panels (paid off) & new A/C!!!  Start your new chapter in this lovely home!   Call today for your PRIVATE showing!
